---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Industrial Safety System">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="relative h-[300px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092580497-e0d23cbdf1dc?w=1600" 
        alt="Industrial Safety" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Industrial Safety System</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <h2>Advanced PPE Detection System</h2>
      <p>Our Industrial Safety System uses state-of-the-art AI to monitor and enforce workplace safety protocols. The system can detect various types of personal protective equipment (PPE) including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hard hats</li>
        <li>Safety glasses</li>
        <li>High-visibility vests</li>
        <li>Safety gloves</li>
        <li>Steel-toed boots</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Real-time Monitoring</h2>
      <p>The system provides real-time alerts when safety violations are detected, allowing immediate intervention and preventing potential accidents before they occur.</p>

      <div class="my-8">
        <h2>See It In Action</h2>
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ"
            title="Product Demo"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            class="w-full h-[400px]"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>